description:
Its weird....instead of the spark of excitement I usually get from connecting dots....this one really makes this real. Look at the nurse’s face in slide 2 & 3 - that’s the face of a nurse comforting a CHILD. I can’t imagine someone with Covid-19 being so sick that they need intravenous fat emulsions.... These photos were some of the first to be released by the US Navy twitter of some of USNS Mercy’s first patients being brought on board.

Sickening. America find your love and compassion for each other because we’re about need it in floods. .
